},{value:"2 Uses",label:"Weekly treatment + as-needed enhancement"}]},howItWorks:{heading:"How it works",activation:{title:"Dual-action mechanism",paragraphs:["Precision Collagen Activation Syringe utilises a two-phase approach. Upon application, the botanical peptide complex begins working at the surface level to support the visible appearance of smoother, more refined skin. This phase is designed to provide visible enhancement that may be observed from the first use and can last throughout the day.","Simultaneously, the hydrolyzed collagen (hydrolyzed collagen) begins working at the skin level to support the skin's natural repair and renewal processes. This progressive phase builds over time with consistent weekly application, supporting longer-term visible improvement in skin texture, firmness, and overall appearance."]},ingredients:{title:"Key ingredient system",items:[{name:"hydrolyzed collagen (Hydrolyzed collagen)",description:"Helps improve the appearance of skin elasticity and smoothness, providing a conditioning and softening effect to targeted areas."},{name:"Botanical Extract Complex",description:"A calming blend of witch hazel, calendula, chamomile, horse chestnut, and peppermint extracts, combined with yarrow, mallow, linden, and St. John's Wort — helping tone, soothe, and comfort the skin."},{name:"Botanical Signal Peptides",description:"Rose flower water and chamomile flower water provide soothing and refreshing properties, helping revitalise the skin and enhance comfort."}]}},protocol:{heading:"Usage protocol",intro:"Precision Collagen Activation Syringe follows a structured correction protocol. Two approaches: weekly treatment for long-term support, and as-needed application for immediate visible enhancement.",steps:[{title:"Weekly treatment",body:"For long-term cellular support, apply once per week to targeted areas. Twist the base to dispense a small amount to the applicator tip. Apply directly to expression lines and areas of visible concern."},