limate control."},{title:"Mineral delivery system",body:"Contains a Pyrenean mineral water — essential ions including zinc, selenium, and copper — that support enzymatic activity and the skin's natural electrical balance."},{title:"Daytime hydration",body:"Provides sustained surface hydration without heaviness. The lightweight texture is designed to absorb quickly, providing a smooth base for subsequent products or makeup."}]},whatItIs:{heading:"What this product is designed to support",benefits:["Helps protect the skin from environmental stressors encountered during the day","Designed to support sustained surface hydration without heaviness or residue","Formulated to deliver essential minerals that support the skin's natural balance","Provides antioxidant support against free radical damage from environmental exposure","Creates a smooth, hydrated base for the rest of your daytime routine","Suitable for daily external application on facial skin"]},howItWorks:{heading:"How it works",activation:{title:"Protection mechanism",paragraphs:["Environmental Shield Day Cream forms a breathable protective film on the skin surface. This film is designed to help shield against environmental particles and reduce moisture loss throughout the day.","The Pyrenean mineral water works at the skin level to support the skin's enzymatic defence systems. These minerals are essential cofactors for antioxidant enzymes that help neutralise free radicals generated by UV exposure and pollution."]},ingredients:{title:"Key ingredient system",items:[{name:"Pyrenean Mineral Complex",description:"Pyrenean mineral water from the Andorran springs forms the aqueous base, carrying naturally occurring trace minerals that help support the skin's natural balance.ymatic activity."},{name:"Antioxidant Support Complex",description:"Red algae extract helps improve hydration and enhances skin smoothness, while cucumber extract provides a refreshing, soothing effect."},{name:"Sustained Hydration Matrix",description:"Sweet almond oil, rich in fatty acids, deeply nourishes and helps protect the skin barrier. Shea butter provides emollient hydration and softness."}]}},protocol:{heading:"Usage protocol",intro:"Environmental Shield Day Cream follows a structured morning application protocol. It is the protective step that seals in the treatment layers while preparing the skin for the day ahead.",steps:[{title:"Morning application",body:"Apply to face and neck every morning after The Serum. Use a pea-sized amount — sufficient to cover the entire face without excess."},{title:"Gentle upward massage",body:"Massage gently in upward motions. This supports circulation and ensures even distribution without pulling the skin downward."},{title:"Allow to set",body:"Wait 2–3 minutes before applying sunscreen or makeup. This allows the protective film to form and the minerals to begin their work."},{title:"Reapply if needed",body:"In extremely dry or harsh environments, a light reapplication mid-day can help maintain the protective barrier and hydration levels."}],summary:[{label:"Frequency",value:"Every morning"},{label:"Amount",value:"Pea-sized"},{label:"Application",value:"Face and neck"},{label:"Set time",value:"2–3 minutes"},{label:"Protocol position",value:"Step 4 of 6"}]},important:{heading:"Important guidelines",intro:"Follow these guidelines to ensure optimal conditions for the daytime protection protocol.",do:["Apply every morning after The Serum","Use upward massage motions","Allow 2–3 minutes before SPF or makeup","Apply to face and neck","Reapply lightly in harsh environments if needed"],avoid:["Skipping this step — protection is essential","Using too much product — a pea-sized amount is sufficient","Applying without prior serum treatment","Rubbing vigorously — gentle application is key","Forgetting SPF — this cream is not a sunscreen replacement"],warning:{title:"Not a sunscreen",body:"Environmental Shield Day Cream is designed to support the skin's defence against environmental stressors but is not a substitute for sunscreen. We recommend applying a broad-spectrum SPF after the cream has set. External use only."}},comparison:{heading:"Why it's different",intro:"Environmental Shield Day Cream represents a distinct approach to daytime skincare — environmental protection with mineral support rather than basic moisturisation.",traditional:{label:"Standard moisturisers",heading:"Basic hydration approach",items:["Primarily hydrates the surface","Limited environmental protection","Generic moisturising ingredients","Short-term hydration that fades","One-size-fits-all formulation"]},product:{label:"Environmental Shield Day Cream",heading:"Mineral environmental protection",items:["Supports defence against environmental stressors","Pyrenean mineral water for enzymatic support","Sustained hydration throughout the day","Lightweight, breathable protective film","Designed as part of an integrated protocol"]}},faq:[{q:"Does it contain SPF?",a:"No, Environmental Shield Day Cream does not contain SPF. It is designed as a protective layer that works alongside sunscreen. We recommend applying a broad-spectrum SPF after the cream has absorbed (2–3 minutes after application)."},{q:"Is it heavy or greasy?",a:"Environmental Shield Day Cream is formulated with a lightweight texture designed to absorb quickly without residue. It provides sustained hydration without the heaviness associated with traditional rich creams."},{q:"Can I wear makeup over it?",a:"Yes. After allowing 2–3 minutes for absorption, Environmental Shield Day Cream provides a smooth, hydrated base for makeup application. The lightweight texture is designed not to interfere with foundation or other cosmetic products."},{q:"How long does one jar last?",a:"With daily morning use of a pea-sized amount, one jar is designed to last approximately 2–3 months."},{q:"Do I need to reapply during the day?",a:"In normal conditions, once-daily morning application is sufficient. In extremely dry, polluted, 