shea butter complex designed to support the structural rebuilding processes that occur during sleep, promoting the appearance of firmer, more resilient skin over time."},{title:"Deep restorative hydration",body:"A richer texture than the Environmental Shield Day Cream, designed to provide sustained hydration throughout the night without transferring to pillows or feeling heavy."}]},whatItIs:{heading:"What this product is designed to support",benefits:["Supports the skin's natural overnight repair and renewal processes","Designed to promote the appearance of firmer, more resilient skin over time","Formulated to provide deep, sustained hydration throughout the night","Helps support the skin's natural barrier recovery during sleep","Works in harmony with the skin's circadian renewal cycle","Suitable for nightly external application on facial and neck skin"]},howItWorks:{heading:"How it works",activation:{title:"Overnight mechanism",paragraphs:["During sleep, the skin's skin renewal processes are at their peak. Blood flow increases, cell turnover accelerates, and the skin enters a state of repair. Renewal and Repair Night Cream is formulated to support and enhance this natural window of renewal.","The hydrolyzed collagen and shea butter complex work together — hydrolyzed collagen supports skin comfort signalling while ceramides help rebuild the lipid barrier that may have been compromised during the day by environmental exposure. This dual approach supports both repair and protection."]},ingredients:{title:"Key ingredient system",items:[{name:"hydrolyzed collagen + Shea Butter Complex",description:"Hydrolyzed collagen helps improve the appearance of elasticity and firmness. Shea butter and sweet almond oil provide deep nourishment and barrier support.wal cycle."},{name:"Overnight Repair Peptides",description:"Niacinamide helps improve skin texture and tone, supporting the skin barrier and contributing to a more even-looking complexion."},{name:"Restorative Lipid Matrix",description:"Lavender floral water provides a gentle aromatic and soothing sensation, contributing to a relaxing nighttime skincare experience."}]}},protocol:{heading:"Usage protocol",intro:"Renewal and Repair Night Cream follows a structured evening application protocol. It is the final step in the Longevity Protocol, designed to seal in all treatment layers and support overnight renewal.",steps:[{title:"Evening application",body:"Apply as the final step in your evening routine, after The Serum. Use a slightly larger amount than the Environmental Shield Day Cream — approximately a almond-sized amount for face and neck."},{title:"Gentle massage",body:"Massage gently into face and neck using upward motions. Take your time — this is a moment of care, not a race."},{title:"Allow to absorb",body:"Allow 5–10 minutes for the cream to fully absorb before lying down. This prevents product transfer and ensures the active compounds begin their overnight work."},{title:"Sleep and renew",body:"The cream works while you sleep. During the 6–8 hours of sleep, the formulation supports the skin's natural repair and renewal processes."}],summary:[{label:"Frequency",value:"Every evening"},{label:"Amount",value:"Almond-sized"},{label:"Application",value:"Face and neck"},{label:"Absorption time",value:"5–10 minutes"},{label:"Protocol position",value:"Step 5 of 6"}]},important:{heading:"Important guidelines",intro:"Follow these guidelines to ensure optimal conditions for the overnight repair protocol.",do:["Apply as the final step in your evening routine","Use upward massage motions on face and neck","Allow 5–10 minutes before lying down","Apply to slightly damp skin for enhanced absorption","Use consistently every night for progressive results"],avoid:["Applying and immediately going to bed","Using too little — the Renewal and Repair Night Cream needs sufficient coverage","Layering additional products on top","Skipping nights — consistency supports the circadian rhythm","Applying to the eye area — use a separate eye product"],warning:{title:"External use only",body:"Renewal and Repair Night Cream is designed exclusively for external facial and neck application. Avoid contact with eyes. If irritation occurs, discontinue use and consult a healthcare professional."}},comparison:{heading:"Why it's different",intro:"Renewal and Repair Night Cream represents a distinct approach to overnight care — specialised regenerative support rather than simply a heavier moisturiser.",traditional:{label:"Standard Renewal and Repair Night Creams",heading:"Heavier version of Environmental Shield Day Cream",items:["Simply a richer moisturiser","Generic hydration without targeted repair","Not aligned with circadian renewal cycle","Limited active ingredients","Basic overnight moisture"]},product:{label:"Renewal and Repair Night Cream",heading:"Overnight regenerative treatment",items:["Supports skin's natural overnight repair cycle","hydrolyzed collagen + ceramides for cellular and barrier support","Works with circadian renewal rhythm","Deep restorative hydration","Final step in integrated 6-step protocol"]}},faq:[{q:"Why do I need a separate Renewal and Repair Night Cream?",a:"The skin's needs differ between day and night. During the day, the skin needs protection from environmental stressors. At night, the skin enters a repair mode with increased cell turnover. Renewal and Repair Night Cream is specifically formulated to support these overnight renewal processes."},{q:"Can I use my Environmental Shield Day Cream at night?",a:"While you can, the Environmental Shield Day Cream is formulated for environmental protection — a function you don't need while sleeping. Renewal and Repair Night Cream contains hydrolyzed collagen and ceramides specifically designed to support the overnight repair cycle. For optimal protocol results, use the designated night formulation."},{q:"Will it stain my pillowcase?",a:"Renewal and Repair Night Cream is designed to absorb fully within 5–10 minutes. We recommend applying it before your evening wind-down routine (reading, meditation, etc.) to allow full absorption before lying down."},{q:"How long does one jar last?",a:"With nightly use of an almond-sized amount, one jar is designed to last approximately 2–3 months."},{q:"Is it too rich for oily skin?",a:"Renewal and Repair Night Cream has a richer texture than Environmental Shield Day Cream by design — the skin can tolerate and benefits from more nourishment overnight. However, if you have very oily skin, start with a smaller amount and adjust as needed."},{q:"Can I use it with retinol?",a:"The Longevity Protocol is designed as a complete system. If you currently use retinol, we recommend transitioning to the full protocol for a structured approach. If you wish to combine, use retinol and Renewal and Repair Night Cream on alternate nights."},{q:"What is the circadian renewal cycle?",a:"The skin follows a circadian rhythm — a 24-hour cycle. During daylight hours, the skin is in defence mode. At night, blood flow increases, cell turnover accelerates, and repair processes activate. Renewal and Repair Night Cream is formulated to support this natural nighttime repair window."},{q:"Should I apply it to my neck too?",a:"Yes. The neck skin is thinner and often shows signs of ageing earlier than the face. Apply Renewal and Repair Night Cream to both face and neck using upward massage motions for comprehensive overnight support."}],cta:{title:"Renew while you sleep",description:"Support your skin's natural overnight repair cycle. One jar. Every evening. Morning-after refinement."}},"syringe-refill":{slug:"syringe-refill",name:"Precision Collagen Activation Refill",subtitle:"Treatment Continuation Cartridge",eyebrow:"Step 06 · Continuation",heroDescription:"A continuation cartridge for the Precision Collagen Activation Syringe applicator. Same Advanced Skin Correction Treatment formulation at a significantly reduced price — exclusively available to Syringe owners